{"word":"διατρέχω","slug":"διατρέχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διατρέχω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-θρέξομαι</el>) (aor2 <el>-έδρᾰμον</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-δεδράμηκα</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to run across</i> or <i>over</i> the sea, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to run through</i>, <el>τὸν βίον, τὸν λόγον</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to run about</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>discurrere</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>δ. μέχρι</el> <i>to penetrate</i> to, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}